OAPS - Online Assessment Proctoring System

## Project Nature
Academic Final Year Project
Runs fully on localhost.
Single professional dashboard interface with role-based views (Interviewer / Interviewee).

## Core Architecture Rules

- Next.js 16 App Router
- TypeScript everywhere
- MongoDB Atlas for user data (auth only)
- In-memory session store (client Zustand + server-side bridge for cross-role data)
- Modular AI architecture
- Strict separation of concerns

## Authentication

- Two roles: **Interviewer** (proctor) and **Interviewee** (candidate)
- Signup: name, email, password, role. Passwords hashed (bcrypt). Users stored in MongoDB.
- Login / Logout: JWT in httpOnly cookie; middleware protects routes
- Route protection: Interviewers cannot access `/interviewee`; Interviewees cannot access `/interviewer`

## Multi-Role Routing

- **Interviewee page** (`/interviewee`): Webcam panel, AI monitoring (TensorFlow.js), session controls. Monitoring runs only here; camera and models disposed on leave.
- **Interviewer page** (`/interviewer`): Risk score dashboard, event logs, session analytics, Gemini AI analysis results. No webcam; data comes from server-side store (synced by interviewee).

## Real-Time Data Flow

- Interviewee: `useSessionSync` batches events + risk + focusRatio to `POST /api/session/events`; session status to `PUT /api/session/status`
- Server: In-memory session store (no DB for session data)
- Interviewer: `useInterviewerData` polls `GET /api/session/events` (~1s) and displays metrics + Gemini report button

## AI Performance Rules

- Use TensorFlow.js WebGL backend
- Lazy-load models
- Process every 2nd frame
- Maintain >= 24 FPS
- Confidence threshold >= 0.65
- Handle model load failures gracefully

## Logging Rules

- All events timestamped
- Categorize: gaze, screen, object
- Never store raw video
- Summarize before report

## Dashboard Rules

- Blue Elegant theme
- Animated real-time metrics
- Color-coded alerts
- Clean academic UI
- Separate dashboards for Interviewer and Interviewee
- Interviewee controls session start/end only
- Interviewer controls session data clearing and AI report generation

## Gemini Rules

- Trigger manually via button (on Interviewer page only)
- Send only summarized metrics
- Never send raw event stream
- Handle API failure gracefully

## Error Handling

- Webcam permission denial fallback
- Model loading spinner
- Fail-safe monitoring stop
- Session reset capability
